kiwiNote.title: KiwiNote
kiwiNote.description: Developed an LLM powered note-taking web application that allows users to record audio, transcribe it, and generate notes.

rateMyUMNDorm.title: RateMyUMNDorm
rateMyUMNDorm.description: Developed a full-stack web application enabling students to review, rate, and explore dormitories at the University of Minnesota.

tuneSwipe.title: TuneSwipe
tuneSwipe.description: Developed a music discovery web application inspired by Tinder, allowing users to swipe through songs and personalize their song feed.

spotimix.title: SpotiMix
spotimix.description: Developed a web application to recommend and display personalized music tracks using the Spotify API.
